targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  max(block_height) AS "block_height"
FROM block_task_pool where sync_status=2

SELECT
  sum(tx_count)
FROM block_detail_info

SELECT
  block_timestamp AS "time",
  block_height
FROM block_detail_info
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(block_timestamp)
ORDER BY block_timestamp

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(depot_updatetime) DIV 1 * 1 AS "time",
  count(pk_id) as value
FROM block_task_pool where sync_status=2 
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1
SELECT block_height, certainty, sync_status, handle_item, depot_updatetime from block_task_pool;
SELECT block_height, contract_name, method_name, block_timestamp from block_tx_detail_info order by block_height;
SELECT block_height, contract_name, contract_address, block_timestamp from account_info;
